  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Introduction"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We need to have Multicore mode handling in slave cores as well, so that respective CDDs/Services in slave core can Init their modules based on EcuM modes"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Solution 1: Mode Handling with BswM running only in Master Core"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We will have BswM running in Master core and Service.EcuModeManager will have Master-Satellite approach"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Multicore%20Mode%20Handling/UC6_ModeHandlingInSlaveCores_WithBswMonMastreCore.bmp?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Multicore Mode Handling/UC6_ModeHandlingInSlaveCores_WithBswMonMastreCore.bmp"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Vector recommended not to use BswM in Multi core aspect due to performance issue."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Solution 2: Mode Handling with Multi core BswM"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We will have BswM running in all cores and mode sync will happen between BswM partition itself"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Multicore%20Mode%20Handling/UC6_ModeHandlingInSlaveCores_WithBswMMultiPartition.bmp?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Multicore Mode Handling/UC6_ModeHandlingInSlaveCores_WithBswMMultiPartition.bmp"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Decision"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "latest Vector SIP (from R28) BswM has an improved performance for Multicore handling. Hence we will go with Solution 2: Mode Handling with Multi core BswM since it is best Autosar way of handling modes"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Reference links:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Mode Synchronization across Cores - XC-CT Cerberus Platform - Docupedia (bosch.com)"
    }
  ],
